  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container-narrow">

    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="https://byagentx.com">byagentx.com</a>
      <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
      <span class="breadcrumb-current" data-lang="es">Casos de éxito</span>
      <span class="breadcrumb-current" data-lang="en">Case studies</span>
      <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
      <span class="breadcrumb-current">La Mesa</span>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-label" data-lang="es">🍽️ Restaurante · Puebla, México</div>
    <div class="hero-label" data-lang="en">🍽️ Restaurant · Puebla, Mexico</div>

    <div data-lang="es">
      <h1>Cómo un restaurante de Puebla <span class="gradient-text">triplicó sus pedidos</span> con un bot de WhatsApp</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">La Mesa pasó de perder pedidos a altas horas de la noche a operar 24/7 de forma automática. Menos estrés, más ingresos, sin contratar más personal.</p>
    </div>
    <div data-lang="en">
      <h1>How a Puebla restaurant <span class="gradient-text">tripled its orders</span> with a WhatsApp bot</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">La Mesa went from missing late-night orders to running 24/7 on autopilot. Less stress, more revenue, no extra staff.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong data-lang="es">Industria:</strong><strong data-lang="en">Industry:</strong>&nbsp;<span data-lang="es">Restaurante / Comida a domicilio</span><span data-lang="en">Restaurant / Food delivery</span></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-dot"></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong data-lang="es">Tamaño:</strong><strong data-lang="en">Size:</strong>&nbsp;<span data-lang="es">5–12 empleados</span><span data-lang="en">5–12 employees</span></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-dot"></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong data-lang="es">Implementación:</strong><strong data-lang="en">Deployed:</strong>&nbsp;<span>7 días / days</span></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-dot"></div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong>ROI:</strong>&nbsp;<span data-lang="es">Primer mes</span><span data-lang="en">First month</span></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Metrics Band -->
    <div class="metrics-band">
      <div class="metric-cell">
        <div class="metric-value green">+40%</div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          <strong data-lang="es">Pedidos online</strong>
          <strong data-lang="en">Online orders</strong>
          <span data-lang="es">vs. mes anterior</span>
          <span data-lang="en">vs. prior month</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-cell">
        <div class="metric-value purple">24/7</div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          <strong data-lang="es">Atención automatizada</strong>
          <strong data-lang="en">Automated support</strong>
          <span data-lang="es">sin descanso</span>
          <span data-lang="en">non-stop</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-cell">
        <div class="metric-value blue">−3h</div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          <strong data-lang="es">Admin por día</strong>
          <strong data-lang="en">Admin per day</strong>
          <span data-lang="es">recuperadas</span>
          <span data-lang="en">reclaimed</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ─── CHALLENGE ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="client-profile">
      <!-- Client card -->
      <div>
        <div class="section-label label-orange" data-lang="es">El desafío</div>
        <div class="section-label label-orange" data-lang="en">The challenge</div>
        <h2 data-lang="es">Un restaurante sólido, ahogado en mensajes</h2>
        <h2 data-lang="en">A solid restaurant drowning in messages</h2>
        <p class="section-desc" data-lang="es">La Mesa era exitoso en sabor pero fallaba en operaciones. Su único canal de pedidos era WhatsApp personal del dueño — y eso se convirtió en su mayor cuello de botella.</p>
        <p class="section-desc" data-lang="en">La Mesa was great at food but failing at operations. Their only ordering channel was the owner's personal WhatsApp — and that became their biggest bottleneck.</p>

        <div class="challenge-list" style="margin-top: 32px;">
          <div class="challenge-item">
            <div class="challenge-icon">😴</div>
            <div class="challenge-text">
              <strong data-lang="es">Pedidos perdidos de noche</strong>
              <strong data-lang="en">Orders lost at night</strong>
              <span data-lang="es">El dueño no podía responder WhatsApp 24/7. Clientes se iban con la competencia.</span>
              <span data-lang="en">The owner couldn't reply to WhatsApp 24/7. Customers went to competitors.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="challenge-item">
            <div class="challenge-icon">⏰</div>
            <div class="challenge-text">
              <strong data-lang="es">3+ horas diarias en admin</strong>
              <strong data-lang="en">3+ hours daily on admin</strong>
              <span data-lang="es">Confirmar pedidos, dar precios, responder horarios — todo manual, todo repetitivo.</span>
              <span data-lang="en">Confirming orders, sharing prices, answering hours — all manual, all repetitive.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="challenge-item">
            <div class="challenge-icon">📉</div>
            <div class="challenge-text">
              <strong data-lang="es">Cero datos de clientes</strong>
              <strong data-lang="en">Zero customer data</strong>
              <span data-lang="es">Sin historial, sin seguimiento, sin forma de saber quién era cliente frecuente.</span>
              <span data-lang="en">No history, no tracking, no way to know who were repeat customers.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="challenge-item">
            <div class="challenge-icon">🤯</div>
            <div class="challenge-text">
              <strong data-lang="es">Errores en pedidos</strong>
              <strong data-lang="en">Order errors</strong>
              <span data-lang="es">Los mensajes de voz y texto mezclados causaban errores frecuentes en cocina.</span>
              <span data-lang="en">Mixed voice and text messages caused frequent kitchen errors.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Client card -->
      <div>
        <div class="client-card">
          <div class="client-avatar">🍽️</div>
          <div class="client-name">La Mesa</div>
          <div class="client-location">📍 Puebla, México</div>
          <div class="client-tags">
            <span class="tag">Restaurante</span>
            <span class="tag">Comida mexicana</span>
            <span class="tag">Delivery</span>
            <span class="tag">Para llevar</span>
            <span class="tag">PYME</span>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
            <!-- Placeholder visual: restaurant illustration -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a00, #2d1500); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,53,0.2);">
              <div style="font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">🌮🌯🍜</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-3);" data-lang="es">Especialidad: Cocina poblana auténtica</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-3);" data-lang="en">Specialty: Authentic Pueblan cuisine</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-3); margin-top: 8px;" data-lang="es">Fundado: 2018 · 4.8 ⭐ en Google</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-3); margin-top: 8px;" data-lang="en">Founded: 2018 · 4.8 ⭐ on Google</div>
            </div>
            <!-- Stats mini -->
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">
              <div style="background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800;">~80</div>
                <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-3);" data-lang="es">pedidos/semana<br>antes de AgentX</div>
                <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-3);" data-lang="en">orders/week<br>before AgentX</div>
              </div>
              <div style="background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-3);">~112</div>
                <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-3);" data-lang="es">pedidos/semana<br>después de AgentX</div>
                <div style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-3);" data-lang="en">orders/week<br>after AgentX</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ─── BEFORE / AFTER ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section>
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
      <div class="section-label label-purple" data-lang="es">La transformación</div>
      <div class="section-label label-purple" data-lang="en">The transformation</div>
      <h2 data-lang="es">De caos en WhatsApp a sistema automatizado</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="en">From WhatsApp chaos to automated system</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="before-after">
      <div class="ba-panel before">
        <div class="ba-header"><div class="ba-dot-red"></div> <span data-lang="es">Antes de AgentX</span><span data-lang="en">Before AgentX</span></div>
        <div class="ba-items">
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">El dueño respondía mensajes hasta medianoche</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Owner replied to messages until midnight</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Menú enviado como imagen por cada cliente</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Menu sent as image to every customer</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Sin confirmación automática de pedidos</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">No automatic order confirmation</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Errores de cocina por mensajes confusos</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Kitchen errors from confusing messages</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Sin datos de clientes recurrentes</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">No recurring customer data</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Imposible manejar picos de demanda</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Unable to handle demand spikes</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-panel after">
        <div class="ba-header"><div class="ba-dot-green"></div> <span data-lang="es">Después de AgentX</span><span data-lang="en">After AgentX</span></div>
        <div class="ba-items">
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Bot responde y toma pedidos 24/7</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Bot responds and takes orders 24/7</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Menú interactivo con categorías y precios</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Interactive menu with categories & prices</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Confirmación + resumen automático al cliente</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Auto confirmation + order summary to client</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Pedidos estructurados directo a cocina</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Structured orders sent directly to kitchen</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">CRM básico: historial y frecuencia</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Basic CRM: history & frequency tracking</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="es">Escala sin límite, sin contratar más</div>
          <div class="ba-item" data-lang="en">Scales without limits, no extra hiring</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ─── SOLUTION ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
      <div class="section-label label-purple" data-lang="es">La solución</div>
      <div class="section-label label-purple" data-lang="en">The solution</div>
      <h2 data-lang="es">Qué implementamos en 7 días</h2>
      <h2 data-lang="en">What we deployed in 7 days</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin: 12px auto 0; text-align: center;" data-lang="es">Sin apps extra, sin hardware, sin cambiar cómo trabaja el restaurante. Solo automatización inteligente.</p>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin: 12px auto 0; text-align: center;" data-lang="en">No extra apps, no hardware, no changing how the restaurant works. Just smart automation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-grid">
      <div class="solution-card">
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="es">Paso 01</div>
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="en">Step 01</div>
        <span class="solution-icon">🤖</span>
        <h3 data-lang="es">Bot de WhatsApp con IA</h3>
        <h3 data-lang="en">AI WhatsApp Bot</h3>
        <p data-lang="es">Responde preguntas frecuentes, presenta el menú, toma pedidos y calcula el total — todo sin intervención humana.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Answers FAQs, presents the menu, takes orders and calculates totals — all without human intervention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-card">
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="es">Paso 02</div>
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="en">Step 02</div>
        <span class="solution-icon">📋</span>
        <h3 data-lang="es">Flujo de pedidos estructurado</h3>
        <h3 data-lang="en">Structured order flow</h3>
        <p data-lang="es">Cada pedido genera una ficha clara para cocina con platillos, personalización y datos de entrega — sin errores de interpretación.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Each order generates a clear kitchen ticket with dishes, customizations and delivery info — no misinterpretation errors.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-card">
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="es">Paso 03</div>
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="en">Step 03</div>
        <span class="solution-icon">🔔</span>
        <h3 data-lang="es">Notificaciones al equipo</h3>
        <h3 data-lang="en">Team notifications</h3>
        <p data-lang="es">El dueño y cocina reciben alertas instantáneas en su propio WhatsApp — sin tener que revisar un sistema nuevo.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Owner and kitchen receive instant alerts on their own WhatsApp — no need to learn a new system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-card">
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="es">Paso 04</div>
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="en">Step 04</div>
        <span class="solution-icon">📊</span>
        <h3 data-lang="es">Dashboard de pedidos</h3>
        <h3 data-lang="en">Orders dashboard</h3>
        <p data-lang="es">Resumen diario automático: cuántos pedidos, platillos más vendidos, ingresos estimados y horas pico.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Daily automatic summary: how many orders, top dishes, estimated revenue and peak hours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-card">
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="es">Paso 05</div>
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="en">Step 05</div>
        <span class="solution-icon">💾</span>
        <h3 data-lang="es">CRM básico de clientes</h3>
        <h3 data-lang="en">Basic customer CRM</h3>
        <p data-lang="es">Registro automático de clientes: nombre, pedidos anteriores y frecuencia. Ideal para promociones futuras.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Automatic customer registration: name, past orders and frequency. Perfect for future promotions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-card">
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="es">Paso 06</div>
        <div class="solution-step" data-lang="en">Step 06</div>
        <span class="solution-icon">🔄</span>
        <h3 data-lang="es">Escalada a humano</h3>
        <h3 data-lang="en">Human handoff</h3>
        <p data-lang="es">Cuando el bot no puede resolver algo, transfiere la conversación al dueño con el contexto completo — sin fricción.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">When the bot can't resolve something, it transfers the conversation to the owner with full context — no friction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

